short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Streamline and accelerate your job search on LinkedIn

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The LinkedIn Job Turbo is a Chrome extension designed to streamline and accelerate your job search on LinkedIn by automating repetitive tasks and enhancing your application workflow. 

With features like auto-filling application forms, navigating seamlessly between job postings, job descriptions (JD) keywords extractions, and automatically downloading JD, this extension enables you to apply for jobs efficiently and keep organized records of each position.
